	<title>Brushing to create a selection</title>
	<purpose>The Brushing tool allows you to use any graphic to create a selection within the map view in ArcMap. You can select a feature by dragging the graphic object so that it overlaps the feature. Selected features update dynamically as the user drags the graphic across the map area. If a graph is created showing the selected features, it gets updated dynamically. </purpose>
